Interface DynamicElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, PointPositioned, ScenarioElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AgentOSM
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Agent, Car, Horse, HorseOSM, Pedestrian, PedestrianOSM

    public interface DynamicElement
extends ScenarioElement, PointPositioned
    Interface for all dynamic elements. Methods from Agent which are shared between all dynamic elements shall shift to this class to provide generalized functionality to all inherited classes.
